text: The material in 4.75.29 is obsolete because the Team Examination Program (TEP) has been discontinued. TEP agents will follow regular examination procedures as outlined in other Exempt Organizations manuals.
IRM 4.75.29, Exempt Organizations Examination Procedures, Exempt Organizations Team Examination Program Procedures dated June 4, 2009 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
